               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18411025-name-1255" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18411025-name-1255" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18411025-name-1255" type="surname" value="HALL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18411025-name-1255" type="given" value="JONATHAN"></interp>JONATHAN HALL</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep the Ship and Whale public-house in Rother-hithe. On the 22nd of September I received some information from one of the customers—in consequence of which I ran out and saw my daughter alongside of the prisoner, bringing him back—I took this glass and knife from him—it was mine—he asked me to allow him to pay for the knife—he had no business with either of them—he had got about 200 yards.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I was not six yards from the house—I was very much in liquor. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> He was not drunk.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18411025-name-1256" type="witnessName">
